java.lang.Object
radin.core.chaining.ToolChainFactory.ToolChainBuilder<T,​R>

public abstract static class ToolChainFactory.ToolChainBuilder<T,​R>
extends Object
implements IToolChain<T,​R>
A tool chain builder is a toolchain that can be expanded upon. Using this class ensures that all parts of a toolchain have the same error collector, and that the objects that are passed through the chain are passed safely.
